<br>
Another thought: If double bolts came back into play, the potential (double bolts + damage focus + crits) means that for SoFB, you COULD do 4510ish damage on <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> one single cast</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> (Max damage, max crit, max 20% bonus for damage focus, calculated twice). Don't you think, with little more investment in your time than standing higher than a mob, you should suddenly be able to double your efficiency? At that point, you outnuke wizards.<br>
<br>
I, personally, am not entirely sure why Raz decided to post his petition. If he doesn't believe in the topic, in my opinion, he should not have been the lead spokesperson on it, and not have scripted up the petition. Being that he did write the petition, I (maybe others) have assumed that Raz actually wants the double bolts back into the game, and I guess that's where the difference of opinion comes from. <p><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=52886">Rhasin Firestorm</A><BR>
